# Coding Conventions

## Naming And Locations

- Components: PascalCase under `src/components/`.
- API routes: `src/app/api/[route]/route.ts`.
- Calculators: `src/lib/calculators/calculate[Name].ts`.
- Prompts: `src/lib/prompts/[type].ts`.

## Response Contract

- Success response:
  - `{ data: { ... }, error: null }`
- Error response:
  - `{ data: null, error: { code, message } }`

## Rendering Model

- Default: Server Component.
- Use Client Component only when required, and add `"use client"` explicitly.

## Supabase Client Split

- Server-side access: `src/lib/supabase/server.ts`.
- Browser-side access: `src/lib/supabase/client.ts`.

## API And Validation Style

- Validate inputs explicitly (zod preferred for API boundaries).
- Return stable error codes (`UNAUTHORIZED`, `VALIDATION_ERROR`, etc.) per API spec.
